posts.post_content:
I have 542 different T206 cards for sale.  All of them listed below.  Unfortunately I couldn't figure out how to sort by last name, so they are all sorted by first name.  High res front and back scans available for all.  Simply go to T206cards.com and search the name or the inventory number (eg 32001234).  Prices listed below are all 10% cheaper than on my site.  Please add $4 for shipping, free if you buy 3 or more cards.  

Also, I am always interested in trades, especially for Polar Bears!
